# Never copy host node_modules into the container — platform-specific native
# binaries (esbuild, etc.) will be wrong architecture (e.g. darwin-arm64 on a
# linux-arm64 container). pnpm install runs inside the container instead.
**/node_modules

# Build outputs — rebuilt inside the container
**/dist
**/.next
**/out
**/.expo

# Test artefacts
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
**/test-results
**/playwright-report

# Dev tools
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Secrets — never bake into an image
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
keys/

# OS / editor noise
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/.vscode
**/.idea
